	building without a previous version installed in ${prefix}/lib.

	* Makefile.am, configure.in, DotGNU.Images/JpegLib.cs.in,
	System.Drawing.Postscript/PostscriptToolkit.cs,
	System.Windows.Forms/Control.cs,
